        <detaileddescription>
<para>Store the last dialog credential returned by vlc_credential_get()</para>
<para>This function will store the credential in the memory keystore if it&apos;s valid, or will store in the permanent one if it comes from the dialog and if the user asked for it.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>true if the credential was stored or comes from the keystore, false otherwise </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
